ic WO stars, we found no line effect and could not sufficiently\nconstrain the rotational velocity to exclude a collapsar scenario. Therefore,\nthe absence of a line effect may not necessarily equate to a low rotational\nvelocity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 16:53:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-19"}
