olved in the video.\nThus, a proof-of-concept for activity recognition using small, IoT based\ndevice, is provided, which can enhance the system and extend its applications\nin various forms like, increase in portability, networking, and other\ncapabilities of the device.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 20:09:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-19"}
