eralizes some particular cases of the literature\nwhen $\\Omega$, $\\omega_c$, $\\Phi$, $s$ or $\\eta$ are excluded from the system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jun 2019 04:15:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 12 Sep 2020 02:56:11 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-15"}
