e matrix is diagonal,\nsymmetric, doubly stochastic, etc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 18 Jun 2019 06:25:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 19 Feb 2022 04:26:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-22"}
