t single-array results, the proposed framework\nhas achieved relative WER reduction of 3.7% and 9.7% in AMI and DIRHA\nmulti-array corpora, respectively, which also outperforms conventional fusion\nstrategies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Jun 2019 23:00:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 18 Oct 2019 18:47:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-22"}
